## üéØ Component Design System

### Buttons

#### Primary Button
```css
.btn-primary {
  background: var(--sunset-coral);
  color: var(--scorecard-white);
  border: 2px solid var(--sunset-coral);
  border-radius: 0.75rem;
  padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
